text: Musaffah Port (Arabic: ميناء مصفّح) is an Abu Dhabi Ports' port located in the industrial town of Musaffah south west of the city of Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates.https://uaetiming.com/e102-bus-timings/ == Developing Musaffah == The interest increased in developing Abu Dhabi's nearby township of Mussafah as an industrial centre during a period of local restoration. Abu Dhabi Seaports Authority announced a Dh2.4 billion development plan of the area. == References == Category:Ports and harbours
title: Musaffah Port
